&lt;/blockquote></description></item><item><title>ShuttleCon Third Edition</title><link>https://anuskuskus.me/p/shuttlecon-third-edition/</link><pubDate>Fri, 24 Nov 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://anuskuskus.me/p/shuttlecon-third-edition/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://anuskuskus.me/p/shuttlecon-third-edition/cover.jpg" alt="Featured image of post ShuttleCon Third Edition" />&lt;p>Hey, tech enthusiasts and event aficionados!&lt;/p>
&lt;p>My job isn&amp;rsquo;t just about coding and designing software. I can also do one of the things I like most: Organising events.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Last year, I was one of the speakers at the opening of &lt;a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/2472920/admin/feed/posts/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Empathy.co&lt;/a> ShuttleCon, an event with talks that repeats every few months, each with a fresh theme. It was a fantastic experience!&lt;/p>
&lt;p>I liked it so much that I couldn&amp;rsquo;t help but become part of the organisation team for the second edition in April with &lt;a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/pablocanalsuarez/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Pablo Cañal Suárez&lt;/a>. And now&amp;hellip; we are bringing you the third edition!&lt;/p>
&lt;p>The ShuttleCon is back! This time, we&amp;rsquo;re diving deep into the roots with the theme &amp;ldquo;Mastering the Basics&amp;rdquo;, because you must first have an excellent base to become the best.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>We will have six excellent speakers introducing us to various technologies and themes: &lt;a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/nvigil/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Noelia Vigil Suarez&lt;/a>, &lt;a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/sotoestevez/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Ricardo Soto Estévez&lt;/a>, &lt;a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/andrea-l%C3%B3pez-su%C3%A1rez-5115801ba/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Andrea López Suárez&lt;/a>, &lt;a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ramiro-alvarez-fernandez-3b945b77/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Ramiro Alvarez Fernandez&lt;/a>, &lt;a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/danirofer/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Daniel Rodriguez Ferrero&lt;/a> and &lt;a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/andrea-delgado-alonso-7039b4177/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Andrea Delgado Alonso&lt;/a>.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>The event will be onsite on Empathy.co Headquarters in Gijón, but also streamed on &lt;a class="link" href="https://www.twitch.tv/empathyco" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Twitch&lt;/a>!&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Save the date – November 30th, 17:30 CET. Head to our &lt;a class="link" href="https://socialclub.empathy.co/event/shuttlecon-3rd-edition" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>event page&lt;/a> for more information, the form to attend onsite and the reveal of talks&amp;rsquo; titles. 😉&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Get ready for an evening of tech talk, inspiration, and a surprise or two. See you at ShuttleCon 3.0 🚀🌐&lt;/p>
